  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?q=80&w=1935&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Vancouver skyline with mountains in the background" class="destination-img" />
  <div class="destination-info">
    <h3 class="destination-name">Vancouver</h3>
    <p class="destination-desc">Balance urban life with outdoor adventures in the Pacific Northwest.</p>
  </div>
</article>

    </div>
  </section>
</main>

